's <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../088/Intel_8088.xml">
documentary</link> <it><movie wordnetid="106613686" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../769/3423769.xml">
Burden of Dreams</link></movie>
</it>, about the production of the film, documents these many hardships. Blank's footage, which also appears in Herzog's <it>Portrait Werner Herzog</it> and <it><movie wordnetid="106613686" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../734/2429734.xml">
My Best Fiend</link></movie>
</it> contains some of the only surviving footage of Robards and Jagger in <it>Fitzcarraldo</it> and many scenes documenting the ship's journey over the mountain, along with several episodes of Kinski's raving.</p>

